    • Method Detail

      • isPlaying

        boolean isPlaying()
        Checks if this villager is currently playing with other child villagers. This normally only applies to children villagers.
        Returns:
        True if this villager is playing with other children

      • setPlaying

        void setPlaying(boolean playing)
        Sets this villager to play with other child villagers.

        This usually is only applicable to children villagers that are still considered babies.

        Parameters:
        playing - If this villager should play

      • isTrading

        boolean isTrading()
        Returns true if this villager is currently trading with another Human. A villager is normally unable to trade with multiple HumanEntities at the same time.
        Returns:
        True if this villager is trading with another player

      • getCareer

        Career getCareer()
        Gets the current career of this villager.
        Returns:
        The current career of this villager

      • setCareer

        void setCareer(Career career)
        Sets the current career of this villager.

        Setting the career of a villager may affect the trade offers this villager can give to other human entities. Likewise, this may change the rendering color of this villager.

        Parameters:
        career - The career to set
